<br>
The simple fact of the matter is evils don't PvP in their lower or mid levels unless actually forced to. If they wanted to PvP, they would go look for it... go to everfrost, you can find plenty of goods to kill; go to velious (like anywhere, GD/EW/etc.) and you can find newts to kill (spinfusor and other iggles are the only ones I know who do this). Likewise overthere is the place to find evils 30 - 50 (there is usually several goods or neutrals in their PK'ing).<br>
<br>
